<h2>Resources you will find helpful while in the U.S.</h2>
<p>Things may seem very different in the U.S. compared to your home country, especially in ways you didn't prepare for. It's important for you to learn as much as you can about how things work in the U.S., so that you can adapt better to your home while here, and gain the greatest from your experience.<br /><br />

If you have any problems or questions while you are in the U.S., you can always contact CSB. We're here to help you. Below, are some resources to help you best familiarize yourself with your new surroundings.</p>
